SQS
----
SQS Stands Simple Queuing Service, its an fully managed message queuing system that is used for building microservices, distributed application and serverless applications

Advantage of using SQS 
1. No need to setup infrastructure 
2. no need to install, configure and monitor the queuing software
3. reliable delivery of large volumes of data with higher throughput
4. securely can exchange the sensitive data through the support of encryption
5. scale elastically based on usage
